{"tid":611471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[真正乞衣兜𢲡飯食] 黑漢勒收陀地被拒　飛磚掟爛電腦維修店門","createTime":"2018-03-31T04:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T07:40:11.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"203dedc735a616fbd93082f4c14da9fe4a5c8e6a","tid":611471,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:53:44.000Z","msg":"鰂魚涌發生刑毀案，現場英皇道1032至1044號福昌樓地下一間電腦維修店，凌晨2時許，一名留宿的姓蔡(36歲)東主煮食期間，突聽到爆玻璃聲，前往門口察看，發現玻璃門毀爛，碎片散滿地上，並發現2塊磚頭；與此同時，蔡目睹2名穿黑衫、戴口罩及鴨舌帽男子登上一輛的士逃去，蔡未能追及，只好報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，翻看閉路電視片段。由於店舖早前曾被7名自稱三合會成員的男子，勒索約1.5萬港元保護費，警方懷疑兩案有關連，案件列作勒索、刑事毀壞及自稱三合會成員，由東區警區刑事調查隊第5隊跟進，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180331/bkn-20180331030506467-0331_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180331%2Fbkn-20180331030506467-0331_00822_001.html&d=4%2BrRIQTk%2BJ4g0iBcleXrgXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a7550065\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180331/bkn-20180331030506467-0331_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"62ce54c9a572941326d041a895b480f8da98485c","tid":611471,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一塊玻璃比盡你咪幾百蚊"},{"pid":"f01d16eeb4c2929b6884f9309f25991a1b0a6e96","tid":611471,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T04:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180331/photo/bkn-20180331030506467-0331_00822_001_03p.jpg?20180331114609\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180331%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180331030506467-0331_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20180331114609&h=77301c0e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f3f6e4c2e7e7bad93596faa586db857f42aa16f","tid":611471,"uid":91833,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"62ce54c9a572941326d041a895b480f8da98485c","tid":611471,"uid":113626,"like